From the looks of it, that’s a client’s run bat…
So you’re going to want to look at these lines:
client.java:
Line 10389
Line 3105
Line 10259
Line 11169
Line 6303
and in RSApplet:
Line 6303[/quote]
I can’t identify the missing interface.
